[
  {
    "text": "♪ Mellow instrumental hip-hop ♪ ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=0"
  },
  {
    "text": "♪ ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=4"
  },
  {
    "text": "Hello and welcome.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=10"
  },
  {
    "text": "My name is Sirisha, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=12"
  },
  {
    "text": "and I'm an engineer on the HealthKit team.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=13"
  },
  {
    "text": "Today, there are hundreds of health and fitness apps ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=16"
  },
  {
    "text": "in the App Store that help users get healthy and stay healthy.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=19"
  },
  {
    "text": "And for them all, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=23"
  },
  {
    "text": "HealthKit provides a centralized encrypted database, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=25"
  },
  {
    "text": "so your amazing apps can show your users a cohesive view ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=28"
  },
  {
    "text": "of their health data.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=31"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now, the Workout APIs are some of the most powerful ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=33"
  },
  {
    "text": "that HealthKit provides, and I love them.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=36"
  },
  {
    "text": "For today's video, I've created a sample cycling app ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=39"
  },
  {
    "text": "for Apple Watch to track my cycling workouts.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=42"
  },
  {
    "text": "And for easier access, I would love to mount my iPhone ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=46"
  },
  {
    "text": "on the handlebars to use as a cycling computer.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=49"
  },
  {
    "text": "That way, I can get a quick and easy view ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=53"
  },
  {
    "text": "of the live metrics displayed on my Apple Watch ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=55"
  },
  {
    "text": "without having to take my hands off the handlebars.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=58"
  },
  {
    "text": "HealthKit is introducing new Workout APIs ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=61"
  },
  {
    "text": "to control and mirror active workout sessions ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=63"
  },
  {
    "text": "between Apple Watch and iPhone.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=66"
  },
  {
    "text": "Updating support for cycling workouts ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=69"
  },
  {
    "text": "with the addition of new data types ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=71"
  },
  {
    "text": "for tracking cycling speed, power, cadence, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=73"
  },
  {
    "text": "and functional threshold power, or FTP.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=77"
  },
  {
    "text": "And if that wasn't enough, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=80"
  },
  {
    "text": "HealthKit along with the Health app is now on iPad.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=82"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now, your customers signed into their iCloud account on iPad ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=86"
  },
  {
    "text": "will see their health data synced through HealthKit ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=90"
  },
  {
    "text": "to their iPad.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=92"
  },
  {
    "text": "Just imagine the richer health ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=94"
  },
  {
    "text": "and post-workout experience you can provide.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=95"
  },
  {
    "text": "Today, I'll use my sample app to demonstrate ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=99"
  },
  {
    "text": "how to mirror a workout running on Apple Watch ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=103"
  },
  {
    "text": "with a paired iPhone.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=106"
  },
  {
    "text": "Then, I'll add some code to show you ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=108"
  },
  {
    "text": "how to collect new cycling metrics ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=110"
  },
  {
    "text": "and sync them across devices.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=112"
  },
  {
    "text": "And I'll wrap up with the authorization details ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=114"
  },
  {
    "text": "required to display workouts on iPad.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=117"
  },
  {
    "text": "So let's check out how Apple Watch, iPhone, and iPad ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=121"
  },
  {
    "text": "can work together to provide a great workout experience.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=125"
  },
  {
    "text": "In my example, I'm running the workout on Apple Watch.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=130"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm using a workout session as a centralized object ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=133"
  },
  {
    "text": "to manage its life cycle, starting, pausing, and stopping.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=136"
  },
  {
    "text": "If you're not already familiar with workout sessions, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=140"
  },
  {
    "text": "you might want to watch previous talks, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=143"
  },
  {
    "text": "\"New ways 'to work with Workouts,\" ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=145"
  },
  {
    "text": "and \"Build a workout app for Apple Watch.\" ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=147"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now, for me to control the workout from my iPhone, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=150"
  },
  {
    "text": "I need to get this workout session ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=153"
  },
  {
    "text": "from my Apple Watch to my iPhone.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=155"
  },
  {
    "text": "And to do so, I'll use HealthKit's ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=158"
  },
  {
    "text": "new mirrored session APIs.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=160"
  },
  {
    "text": "When a mirrored session starts on my Apple Watch, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=163"
  },
  {
    "text": "if my iPhone app is not running, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=166"
  },
  {
    "text": "it will be launched in the background ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=168"
  },
  {
    "text": "and handed over the workout session.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=170"
  },
  {
    "text": "To receive the session, my iPhone app needs to be ready.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=172"
  },
  {
    "text": "So, first I'll set up a handler ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=176"
  },
  {
    "text": "in the iPhone app launch sequence using the HealthStore.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=179"
  },
  {
    "text": "That way, it will be ready to receive the session ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=182"
  },
  {
    "text": "from my Apple Watch.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=184"
  },
  {
    "text": "Every time my iPhone app is launched ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=187"
  },
  {
    "text": "in the foreground or the background, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=189"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'll implement the mirroring start handler ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=191"
  },
  {
    "text": "in order to receive the active workout session ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=194"
  },
  {
    "text": "passed from my Apple Watch.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=196"
  },
  {
    "text": "Next, I'll create a workout configuration ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=199"
  },
  {
    "text": "with an activity type of cycling.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=201"
  },
  {
    "text": "Then I'll call the existing Start Watch App API ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=205"
  },
  {
    "text": "in my iPhone app to launch the app on my paired Apple Watch ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=208"
  },
  {
    "text": "and pass the workout configuration.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=213"
  },
  {
    "text": "When I receive the configuration from my iPhone, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=216"
  },
  {
    "text": "I can create a workout session in my Apple Watch app.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=219"
  },
  {
    "text": "The workout session on my Apple Watch ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=222"
  },
  {
    "text": "is called the primary session.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=224"
  },
  {
    "text": "And the workout session on my iPhone ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=226"
  },
  {
    "text": "is called the mirrored session.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=227"
  },
  {
    "text": "So here's how it looks.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=231"
  },
  {
    "text": "When I start a workout in my iPhone app, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=232"
  },
  {
    "text": "my app on my Apple Watch gets launched ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=235"
  },
  {
    "text": "with the configuration sent from my iPhone.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=237"
  },
  {
    "text": "So far, so good.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=240"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now the thing that makes this API so convenient ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=242"
  },
  {
    "text": "is that HealthKit takes care of keeping ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=245"
  },
  {
    "text": "both the primary and the mirrored session states in sync.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=247"
  },
  {
    "text": "For example, when the primary session is paused ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=251"
  },
  {
    "text": "on my Apple Watch, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=253"
  },
  {
    "text": "the mirrored session on my iPhone is paused as well.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=255"
  },
  {
    "text": "In addition to getting a copy of the active workout session ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=259"
  },
  {
    "text": "to my iPhone, HealthKit also provides a new API ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=262"
  },
  {
    "text": "to exchange relevant workout data between both devices, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=266"
  },
  {
    "text": "and provides the ability to begin and end activities ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=271"
  },
  {
    "text": "as well as generate events.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=274"
  },
  {
    "text": "OK, now that I have my primary session ready ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=277"
  },
  {
    "text": "and my iPhone ready to receive the handler, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=280"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'll start mirroring from my Apple Watch ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=283"
  },
  {
    "text": "by calling startMirroringToCompanionDevice ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=285"
  },
  {
    "text": "and start the primary session.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=288"
  },
  {
    "text": "Once I call startMirroring on Apple Watch, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=292"
  },
  {
    "text": "HealthKit launches my companion iPhone app in the background, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=294"
  },
  {
    "text": "gives my app 10 seconds to start a live activity ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=298"
  },
  {
    "text": "and call a handler to start mirroring.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=301"
  },
  {
    "text": "Great, so we have started the session on the Apple Watch ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=304"
  },
  {
    "text": "and got the copy on iPhone.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=307"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now, let me show you how the session state ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=310"
  },
  {
    "text": "is communicated between the devices.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=312"
  },
  {
    "text": "In my example app, I want to show my users ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=315"
  },
  {
    "text": "the state of the workout session, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=318"
  },
  {
    "text": "like whether the session is running, paused, et cetera.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=320"
  },
  {
    "text": "So I'll set up the session delegate on Apple Watch ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=324"
  },
  {
    "text": "and iPhone to monitor the session state updates ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=327"
  },
  {
    "text": "and the events generated.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=330"
  },
  {
    "text": "Keep in mind that it is important to keep a reference ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=333"
  },
  {
    "text": "to the retrieved mirrored session on the iPhone app.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=336"
  },
  {
    "text": "Calling startActivity on my Apple Watch ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=341"
  },
  {
    "text": "starts the primary session ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=343"
  },
  {
    "text": "and changes the session state to running.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=345"
  },
  {
    "text": "This state update is delivered to my Apple Watch app ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=347"
  },
  {
    "text": "since it's set as session delegate of the primary session.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=350"
  },
  {
    "text": "My app on my iPhone also gets the state update ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=354"
  },
  {
    "text": "through the mirrored session delegate.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=357"
  },
  {
    "text": "It's that easy to bring an active workout session to iPhone ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=359"
  },
  {
    "text": "and monitor the changes on a session.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=362"
  },
  {
    "text": "So here's what it looks like.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=365"
  },
  {
    "text": "When a workout session is started on my Apple Watch, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=367"
  },
  {
    "text": "the pause button on my iPhone and my Apple Watch ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=370"
  },
  {
    "text": "is activated to indicate that the workout session is running.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=373"
  },
  {
    "text": "In addition to syncing session states ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=378"
  },
  {
    "text": "between the primary and the mirrored session, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=380"
  },
  {
    "text": "I can also generate and send events like pause and resume.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=382"
  },
  {
    "text": "When I pause the workout session on my Apple Watch, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=387"
  },
  {
    "text": "both my Apple Watch app ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=390"
  },
  {
    "text": "and the mirrored session on my iPhone ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=392"
  },
  {
    "text": "get notified about the pause event ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=394"
  },
  {
    "text": "through their session delegate.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=396"
  },
  {
    "text": "And that looks like this.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=399"
  },
  {
    "text": "When I pause a workout session on my Apple Watch, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=401"
  },
  {
    "text": "the resume button on both my devices becomes active.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=403"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now that I have a workout session on my iPhone, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=407"
  },
  {
    "text": "I can control the workout from iPhone as well.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=410"
  },
  {
    "text": "When I resume the mirrored session on my iPhone, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=414"
  },
  {
    "text": "the primary session delegate on my Apple Watch ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=416"
  },
  {
    "text": "gets notified about the state change ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=419"
  },
  {
    "text": "and the mirrored session delegate gets a resume event.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=421"
  },
  {
    "text": "Next, I would like to show you how to take advantage ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=424"
  },
  {
    "text": "of the new cycling features ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=427"
  },
  {
    "text": "HealthKit is introducing this year, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=429"
  },
  {
    "text": "including new data types such as cycling speed, power, cadence; ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=431"
  },
  {
    "text": "a new ability to directly connect to Bluetooth devices ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=437"
  },
  {
    "text": "designed to provide these data types, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=440"
  },
  {
    "text": "similar to how a heart rate monitor collects and writes ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=443"
  },
  {
    "text": "heart rate data to the health database; ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=446"
  },
  {
    "text": "and finally, the ability for HealthKit on Apple Watch ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=449"
  },
  {
    "text": "to automatically calculate and save FTP ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=452"
  },
  {
    "text": "based on the data collected from these Bluetooth devices.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=455"
  },
  {
    "text": "My bike has a power meter that collects power and cadence, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=459"
  },
  {
    "text": "which I paired with my Apple Watch.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=463"
  },
  {
    "text": "The sensor writes the data to my Apple Watch, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=465"
  },
  {
    "text": "and I would like to extend my app to send that data ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=468"
  },
  {
    "text": "to my iPhone for display as I ride.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=471"
  },
  {
    "text": "To do this, I'll first start collecting cycling metrics ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=474"
  },
  {
    "text": "using the recommended workout builder API beginCollection.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=477"
  },
  {
    "text": "And then I'll send the data ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=481"
  },
  {
    "text": "using the sendData(toRemoteWorkoutSession) API.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=482"
  },
  {
    "text": "To send the cycling metrics, I'll package the speed, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=487"
  },
  {
    "text": "cadence, and power data received from Bluetooth sensors ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=490"
  },
  {
    "text": "on my Apple Watch and call ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=493"
  },
  {
    "text": "sendData(toRemoteWorkoutSession) on the primary session.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=495"
  },
  {
    "text": "As a result, the mirrored session delegate on my iPhone ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=499"
  },
  {
    "text": "will receive the didReceiveDataFromRemoteDevice ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=502"
  },
  {
    "text": "call with the package data, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=505"
  },
  {
    "text": "which I can unpack and display on my iPhone.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=507"
  },
  {
    "text": "Here is how it looks like with my example app ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=511"
  },
  {
    "text": "sending cycling metrics from my Apple Watch ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=514"
  },
  {
    "text": "and how they are displayed in my iPhone app.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=516"
  },
  {
    "text": "Using sendData(toRemoteWorkoutSession) ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=520"
  },
  {
    "text": "I can also send data in the opposite direction ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=522"
  },
  {
    "text": "from my iPhone to my Apple Watch.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=525"
  },
  {
    "text": "In my example, I want to keep track of my water intake ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=528"
  },
  {
    "text": "during a workout so I can analyze it afterwards ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=531"
  },
  {
    "text": "in the hopes of creating a better hydration plan ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=534"
  },
  {
    "text": "for my next ride.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=537"
  },
  {
    "text": "To do this, I'll package and send ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=539"
  },
  {
    "text": "the amount of water I consume on the mirrored session ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=541"
  },
  {
    "text": "from my iPhone to Apple Watch.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=544"
  },
  {
    "text": "The primary session's delegate method ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=546"
  },
  {
    "text": "didReceiveDataFromRemoteDevice is called with the packaged data ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=549"
  },
  {
    "text": "which I'll unpack and save on my Apple Watch.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=553"
  },
  {
    "text": "So here's how it looks in my example app.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=558"
  },
  {
    "text": "When I tap the button to count each ounce of water I take, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=561"
  },
  {
    "text": "it sends it to my Apple Watch, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=564"
  },
  {
    "text": "where it displays the total amount of water consumed.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=566"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now I can stop mirroring the session anytime ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=570"
  },
  {
    "text": "during the workout by calling ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=572"
  },
  {
    "text": "stopMirroringToCompanionDevice API.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=574"
  },
  {
    "text": "Calling this method will stop sending data ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=577"
  },
  {
    "text": "to the companion device and the mirrored session's ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=580"
  },
  {
    "text": "didDisconnectFromRemoteDevice WithError delegate method ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=582"
  },
  {
    "text": "will be called.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=586"
  },
  {
    "text": "And when I'm done cycling, I'll end the primary session ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=588"
  },
  {
    "text": "and save it on the Apple Watch by finishing the builder.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=590"
  },
  {
    "text": "After saving the workout sample on Apple Watch, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=594"
  },
  {
    "text": "it syncs to my other devices, and I can now show ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=596"
  },
  {
    "text": "the post-workout summary with more detailed charts ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=599"
  },
  {
    "text": "and visualizations.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=602"
  },
  {
    "text": "Great! My next step is to present the post-workout summary ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=604"
  },
  {
    "text": "in my app running on my iPad.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=608"
  },
  {
    "text": "Since the workout I just saved on Apple Watch ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=611"
  },
  {
    "text": "automatically syncs to iPad, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=613"
  },
  {
    "text": "I only need to make a few changes ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=616"
  },
  {
    "text": "to visualize my workout data.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=618"
  },
  {
    "text": "Like any app accessing HealthKit data, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=620"
  },
  {
    "text": "my app on iPad will will first need to get user authorization.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=622"
  },
  {
    "text": "When an app requests authorization, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=627"
  },
  {
    "text": "the authorization sheet is shown if needed.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=629"
  },
  {
    "text": "On iPad, your app might have multiple window scenes, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=632"
  },
  {
    "text": "so it's important to ensure that the authorization sheet ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=636"
  },
  {
    "text": "is shown over the appropriate scene.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=639"
  },
  {
    "text": "To do this in my app, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=642"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'll first import HealthKitUI framework.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=644"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'll specify the data types I'm interested in reading, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=648"
  },
  {
    "text": "specifically active energy, cycling speed, power, cadence, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=651"
  },
  {
    "text": "heart rate, and workout samples.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=656"
  },
  {
    "text": "Then, since I built a SwiftUI app, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=659"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'll use the new healthDataAccessRequest ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=662"
  },
  {
    "text": "view modifier from the HealthKitUI framework ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=665"
  },
  {
    "text": "and pass the data types I want to share and read, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=669"
  },
  {
    "text": "as well as a trigger.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=671"
  },
  {
    "text": "Setting the trigger to true ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=673"
  },
  {
    "text": "will present the authorization sheet in my app.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=675"
  },
  {
    "text": "For a UIKit app, you would set the ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=679"
  },
  {
    "text": "healthStores.authorizationView ControllerPresenter property, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=681"
  },
  {
    "text": "and then request authorization ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=685"
  },
  {
    "text": "with the types to share and read.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=686"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now, with the authorization taken care of, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=689"
  },
  {
    "text": "let's check out my workout on iPad.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=692"
  },
  {
    "text": "Amazing! ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=695"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now I can access my workout data ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=696"
  },
  {
    "text": "and take advantage of the iPad's screen size ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=698"
  },
  {
    "text": "to create a richer experience for my app.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=701"
  },
  {
    "text": "Isn't it super easy? ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=704"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now you can start and control a workout from your iPhone, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=706"
  },
  {
    "text": "collect and sync rich cycling data from your Apple Watch, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=709"
  },
  {
    "text": "and finally, view the workout details on your iPad.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=713"
  },
  {
    "text": "To wrap up, be sure to update your app ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=716"
  },
  {
    "text": "to support authorization on iPad.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=719"
  },
  {
    "text": "If your Fitness app involves cycling, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=721"
  },
  {
    "text": "you can add support for new data types.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=723"
  },
  {
    "text": "If you build workout apps on iPhone and Apple Watch, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=726"
  },
  {
    "text": "check out the new mirrored session APIs ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=730"
  },
  {
    "text": "to start mirroring data and controlling state ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=732"
  },
  {
    "text": "between both devices.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=735"
  },
  {
    "text": "If your app needs it, use sync identifiers and version numbers ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=737"
  },
  {
    "text": "to keep the data consistent ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=741"
  },
  {
    "text": "across your server and users' devices.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=742"
  },
  {
    "text": "And finally, give us your feedback.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=745"
  },
  {
    "text": "We want to support the features you need ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=748"
  },
  {
    "text": "to keep building those amazing apps to keep the world healthy.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=750"
  },
  {
    "text": "Thank you for watching.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=753"
  },
  {
    "text": "♪",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10023/?time=755"
  }
]